data.description: Welcome to 331 Primrose Way! This stunning home offers a spacious and open floor plan spanning across 2,735 square feet, providing you with an abundance of living space to enjoy. Situated in a desirable location, this residence is designed to offer comfort, style, and versatility.    Upon entering, you'll immediately be captivated by the airy and welcoming ambiance that flows throughout the home. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the main living area, creating an ideal space for both relaxation and entertaining. Natural light pours in through the large windows, enhancing the warm and inviting atmosphere.    The heart of this home is the expansive game room, perfect for hosting gatherings or enjoying quality time with loved ones. Imagine the endless possibilities for fun and entertainment as you engage in lively game nights or indulge in your favorite hobbies.    The living area offers a generous layout, ideal for accommodating various furniture arrangements and creating your desired seating arrangements. Whether you're enjoying a cozy movie night with your family or hosting a get-together with friends, this space effortlessly caters to your needs.    The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting ample counter space, modern appliances, and sleek cabinetry. Prepare delicious meals and savor them in the adjacent dining area, creating a seamless flow for everyday dining or special occasions.    The bedrooms in this home are designed with comfort in mind. Each room provides a serene retreat where you can unwind after a long day. The master suite is particularly impressive, featuring a spacious layout, a well-appointed en-suite bathroom, and a walk-in closet for all your storage needs.    Outside, you'll find a beautifully landscaped yard that offers both privacy and tranquility. This outdoor space presents an excellent opportunity to create your own oasis, whether you envision a lush garden, a serene patio, or a space for outdoor activities.    Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers convenient access to nearby amenities, schools, parks, and shopping centers. With its ideal blend of functionality, style, and entertainment options, 331 Primrose Way is a true gem waiting to be discovered.    As an added bonus, this home comes with a 1-year pest control service included through Simpl Pest Control. You can enjoy peace of mind knowing that your new home is protected from unwanted pests, allowing you to fully relish in your comfortable and pest-free environment.    Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the allure and charm of this spacious residence firsthand.
